{"tid":2516764,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"（扎染）今次染左兩個外國勢力上件衫度","createTime":"2021-05-05T00:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T07:11:19.000Z","uid":235015,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3a730c688007b5d6956af10985bdb1078d155aa9","tid":2516764,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:47:52.000Z","msg":"Hi又係我，一個整扎染既迷途小羔羊<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hair.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次故技重施，又用左件白色Nike衫<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbaEF8m55D4gnPk2fz2W1mLhiPP7E6b7BHpmiW8UFDPZa?filename=Y60faUS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY60faUS.jpg&h=0a7e47da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n普通扎染款一街都係，大家都見得多，所以想唸下可以點樣整得特別d<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以用左呢幅畫黎做今次扎染既概念<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPPpKDhVRdruoYis8ZRWUCvQc8J9PufHHtG3h3R6Jb965?filename=6DUs4Hy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6DUs4Hy.png&h=725658f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n列賓 - 恐怖的伊凡<br />\n<br />\n今次簡單少少，用左兩種扎染手法，正中間位間開兩個區域做背景，同時加上黑白色象徵果兩個外國勢力<br />\n<br />\n附上對比圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmciVDZS2fSaCePNCqSvY1qrBKTuhBbsWrXCiMB9ThJ7p8?filename=RfOEVRb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRfOEVRb.png&h=dfd81360&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家覺得點呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n鐘意既話可以follow下小弟既IG，會不定時整唔同既扎染服飾<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/slient.dye/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fslient.dye%2F&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK7XdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=d4c8fae6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/slient.dye/</a><br />\n歡迎大家交流下心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者大家有咩概念想我整做扎染既都可以話我知，可行情況下會間唔中整下 （例如動漫角色/球隊/任何有顏色既野）<br />\n<br />\n上個post有巴絲俾左唔錯既題材俾我，黎緊有時間會試下整番找數"},{"pid":"51444172816266dcb18620cf798417f32fb0b92a","tid":2516764,"uid":6111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:54:18.000Z","msg":"依d咁花既衫係咪得老mk會著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d38f04133b6b3743472397253c8723ef59c440bc","tid":2516764,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"51444172816266dcb18620cf798417f32fb0b92a","tid":2516764,"uid":6111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:54:18.000Z","msg":"依d咁花既衫係咪得老mk會著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:55:17.000Z","msg":"唔準你咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多後生著"},{"pid":"5179a1de5a2d2ae8aaa77c6fe201c077c3a01cd9","tid":2516764,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:58:06.000Z","msg":"金鐘連登仔先carry得起嘅fashion<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a432657cbf2d8882757d07ffe1923a33f571018","tid":2516764,"uid":262053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T01:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fdcb703198b13897825ae30d5a3f775b21b1008","tid":2516764,"uid":149018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:04:55.000Z","msg":"我諗連登真係99%人無興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0615e243b1625e88795554f1ed818364d191627b","tid":2516764,"uid":396028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:18:12.000Z","msg":"上次梵高個件易接受D"},{"pi